content.rendered:
Paris Fashion Week WOMENSWEAR SPRING/SUMMER 2024 

From September 25th to October 3rd, 2023

The Fdration de la Haute Couture et de la Mode helps to consolidate

Paris in its role as world fashion capital, in particular thanks to

Paris Fashion Week and Haute Couture Week, which it coordinates.

Paris Fashion Week

Womenswear Spring/Summer 2024 Provisional Calendar

More on www.fhcm.paris and @parisfashionweek
